=version 1
=resource User
=method delete
=endpoint /users/:id/2fa
=description Disables two-factor authentication on the user account.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p Hitting this endpoint removes two-factor credentials from a the user account.

h3 Parameters

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name :id
        td.description The numeric user ID.

h3 Possible Results

+result("Successful", "200 OK").
    "Two factor disabled."

+result("Errorful", "403 Forbidden").
    "You are not permitted to perform that action."
